Type: Package
Package: PKbioanalysis
Title: A package for pharmacokinetic bioanalysis design and exploration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Omar", "Elashkar", email = "omar.i.elashkar@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Omar Elashkar <omar.i.elashkar@gmail.com>
Description: PKbioanalysis is a package that aims to automate pharmacokinetic/pharmacodynamic bioanalytical
    procedures based on best practices and regulatory recommendations. The package impose regulatory constrains and sanity checking 
    for common bioanalytical procedures. Additionally, PKbioanalysis provides a relational infrastructure for plate management and injection sequence.
